{
  "spec": {
    "title": "CSS Route Matching",
    "url": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "create a URL pattern for url-pattern()",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern",
      "html": "This function represents a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern②\">URL pattern</a> that can be created\nusing the steps of the <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">create a URL pattern for url-pattern()</dfn> algorithm:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>arg</var> be the <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#string-value\" id=\"ref-for-string-value②\">&lt;string&gt;</a> argument to the <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#funcdef-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-url-pattern⑥\">url-pattern()</a> function.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>baseURL</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-values-4/#style-resource-base-url\" id=\"ref-for-style-resource-base-url①\">style resource base URL</a> of\nthe rule or declaration block containing the <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#funcdef-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-url-pattern⑦\">url-pattern()</a> function.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-create\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-create①\">create a URL pattern</a> given\n<var>arg</var>, <var>baseURL</var>, and an empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map\">map</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "serialize a url-pattern() function",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#serialize-a-url-pattern-function",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-export=\"\" id=\"serialize-a-url-pattern-function\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">serialize a <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#funcdef-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-funcdef-url-pattern①①\">url-pattern()</a> function</dfn> <var>f</var>,\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-1/#css-serialize-a-function\" id=\"ref-for-css-serialize-a-function\">serialize a function</a> <var>f</var>,\nusing <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-1/#serialize-a-string\" id=\"ref-for-serialize-a-string\">serialize a string</a> on the single argument\nto serialize <var>f</var>’s contents.",
      "rationale": "To <dfn>"
    },
    {
      "name": "route-location/match",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#route-location-match",
      "html": "A <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-route-location\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-route-location②\">&lt;route-location&gt;</a> is defined to\n<dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"route-location\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"route-location-match\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">match</dfn> a URL <var>input</var> if:",
      "rationale": ".switch",
      "steps": [
        {
          "operation": "switch",
          "steps": [
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <route-name>",
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match\">match a URL pattern</a> is non-null given\n<var>urlPattern</var> as\nthe <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern③\">URL pattern</a> represented by the <a class=\"css\" data-link-type=\"maybe\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#at-ruledef-route\" id=\"ref-for-at-ruledef-route⑥\">@route</a> rule referenced by the name and\n<var>input</var> as <var>input</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <url-pattern()>",
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match①\">match a URL pattern</a> is non-null given\n<var>urlPattern</var> as\nthe <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern④\">URL pattern</a> represented by the function (see\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern\" id=\"ref-for-create-a-url-pattern-for-url-pattern\">create a URL pattern for url-pattern()</a>) and\n<var>input</var> as <var>input</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "case": "the <route-location> is a <url>",
              "html": "<p>The given URL <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-equals\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-equals\">equals</a> <var>input</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "document’s navigation API",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api",
      "html": "A <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"documents-navigation-api\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">document’s navigation API</dfn> is\nthe result of the following steps on <var>document</var>:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>window</var> be the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window\" id=\"ref-for-window\">Window</a></code> whose <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window\">associated Document</a> is <var>document</var>, or null if there is no such <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window\" id=\"ref-for-window①\">Window</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>window</var> is null, return null.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <var>window</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#window-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-window-navigation-api\">navigation API</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "active navigation URL",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#active-navigation-url",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"active-navigation-url\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">active navigation URL</dfn> for an <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-active-navigation-condition\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-active-navigation-condition③\">&lt;active-navigation-condition&gt;</a> is:",
      "rationale": ".switch",
      "steps": [
        {
          "operation": "switch",
          "steps": [
            {
              "case": "If the <navigation-relation> is at",
              "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-at-url\" id=\"ref-for-current-at-url①\">current at URL</a> of the document"
            },
            {
              "case": "If the <navigation-relation> is with or is omitted",
              "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-with-url\" id=\"ref-for-current-with-url①\">current with URL</a> of the document"
            },
            {
              "case": "If the <navigation-relation> is from",
              "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-from-url\" id=\"ref-for-current-from-url②\">current from URL</a> of the document"
            },
            {
              "case": "If the <navigation-relation> is to",
              "html": "The <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-to-url\" id=\"ref-for-current-to-url②\">current to URL</a> of the document"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "An <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-active-navigation-condition\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-active-navigation-condition④\">&lt;active-navigation-condition&gt;</a> matches the target <var>linkTarget</var> of the link when\nthe following steps return true:",
      "rationale": "let",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>navigationURL</var> be\nthe <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#active-navigation-url\" id=\"ref-for-active-navigation-url\">active navigation URL</a> of the <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-active-navigation-condition\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-active-navigation-condition⑤\">&lt;active-navigation-condition&gt;</a></p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>navigationURL</var> is null, return false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If a <a class=\"css production\" data-link-type=\"type\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#typedef-route-location\" id=\"ref-for-typedef-route-location②④\">&lt;route-location&gt;</a> is present:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>targetMatchResult</var> be the result of\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match②\">match a URL pattern</a>\ngiven <var>urlPattern</var> and <var>linkTarget</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>navigationMatchResult</var> be the result of\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#url-pattern-match\" id=\"ref-for-url-pattern-match③\">match a URL pattern</a> given\n <var>urlPattern</var> and <var>navigationURL</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>navigationMatchResult</var> or <var>targetMatchResult</var> is null, return false.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "For each property <var>prop</var> of <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dictdef-urlpatternresult\" id=\"ref-for-dictdef-urlpatternresult\">URLPatternResult</a></code> that is a\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dictdef-urlpatterncomponentresult\" id=\"ref-for-dictdef-urlpatterncomponentresult\">URLPatternComponentResult</a></code>:",
              "rationale": "if",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups\">groups</a></code> of <var>prop</var> of\n<var>targetMatchResult</var> is not equal to\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://urlpattern.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups\" id=\"ref-for-dom-urlpatterncomponentresult-groups①\">groups</a></code> of <var>prop</var> of\n<var>navigationMatchResult</var>,\nthen return false.</p>"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Return true.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise:",
          "rationale": "return",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Return true if <var>linkTarget</var> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-equals\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-equals①\">equals</a> <var>navigationURL</var>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Return false.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current from URL",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-from-url",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-from-url\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current from URL</dfn> of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document\">document</a> is a URL or null.\nIt is defined as follows:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-navigation-transition\" id=\"ref-for-concept-navigation-transition\">transition</a> is non-null,\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-navigationtransition-from\" id=\"ref-for-concept-navigationtransition-from\">from entry</a>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\">url</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api①\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null,\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigation-activation\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-activation\">activation</a> is non-null,\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from\">from</a></code> is non-null, and\nthe document’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsing-the-web.html#has-been-revealed\" id=\"ref-for-has-been-revealed\">has been revealed</a> is false or\nwas false at the start of the current <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-task\" id=\"ref-for-concept-task\">task</a>,\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from①\">from</a></code>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url①\">url</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current to URL",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-to-url",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-to-url\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current to URL</dfn> of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document①\">document</a> is a URL or null.\nIt is defined as follows:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api②\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#ongoing-navigate-event\" id=\"ref-for-ongoing-navigate-event\">ongoing navigate event</a> is non-null:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>if the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-pageswap\" id=\"ref-for-event-pageswap\">pageswap</a></code> event has fired since that navigation began,\nand its <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-pageswapevent-activation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-pageswapevent-activation\">activation</a></code> was non-null,\nand that <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-pageswapevent-activation\" id=\"ref-for-dom-pageswapevent-activation①\">activation</a></code>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry\">entry</a></code>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url②\">url</a></code> is non-null,\nthen that\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url③\">url</a></code>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>otherwise, the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#ongoing-navigate-event\" id=\"ref-for-ongoing-navigate-event①\">ongoing navigate event</a>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigateevent-destination\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigateevent-destination\">destination</a></code>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationdestination-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationdestination-url\">url</a></code></p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api③\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigation-activation\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-activation①\">activation</a> is non-null,\nthe document’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsing-the-web.html#has-been-revealed\" id=\"ref-for-has-been-revealed①\">has been revealed</a> is false or\nwas false at the start of the current <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-task\" id=\"ref-for-concept-task①\">task</a>,\nand the activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry①\">entry</a></code>’s\n<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-url\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-url④\">url</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation type",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-type",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-type\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation type</dfn> of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document④\">document</a> is a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-navigationtype\">NavigationType</a></code> or null.\nIt is defined as follows:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api④\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-navigation-transition\" id=\"ref-for-concept-navigation-transition②\">transition</a> is non-null,\nthe transition’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtransition-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtransition-navigationtype\">navigationType</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api⑤\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigation-activation\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-activation②\">activation</a> is non-null,\nthe document’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsing-the-web.html#has-been-revealed\" id=\"ref-for-has-been-revealed②\">has been revealed</a> is false or\nwas false at the start of the current <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-task\" id=\"ref-for-concept-task②\">task</a>,\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype\">navigationType</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "current navigation delta",
      "href": "https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#current-navigation-delta",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"current-navigation-delta\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">current navigation delta</dfn> of a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document⑤\">document</a> is a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-navigationtype①\">NavigationType</a></code> or null.\nIt is defined as follows:",
      "rationale": "if",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api⑥\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null and\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-navigation-transition\" id=\"ref-for-concept-navigation-transition③\">transition</a> is non-null,",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If the transition’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtransition-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtransition-navigationtype①\">navigationType</a></code> is not <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtype-traverse\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtype-traverse③\">traverse</a></code>, null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Otherwise,\nthe transition’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtransition-to\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtransition-to\">to</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationdestination-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationdestination-index\">index</a></code>\nminus\nthe transition’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtransition-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtransition-from\">from</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\">index</a></code>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "If the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-navigation-1/#documents-navigation-api\" id=\"ref-for-documents-navigation-api⑦\">document’s navigation API</a> of the document is non-null,\nits <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#navigation-activation\" id=\"ref-for-navigation-activation③\">activation</a> is non-null,\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from③\">from</a></code> is non-null, and\nthe document’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsing-the-web.html#has-been-revealed\" id=\"ref-for-has-been-revealed③\">has been revealed</a> is false or\nwas false at the start of the current <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-task\" id=\"ref-for-concept-task③\">task</a>,",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If the activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-navigationtype①\">navigationType</a></code> is not <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationtype-traverse\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationtype-traverse④\">traverse</a></code>, null.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Otherwise,\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-entry\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-entry②\">entry</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index①\">index</a></code>\nminus\nthe activation’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationactivation-from\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationactivation-from④\">from</a></code>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#dom-navigationhistoryentry-index\" id=\"ref-for-dom-navigationhistoryentry-index②\">index</a></code>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Otherwise, null.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}